title: Jews Failed To ‘Actively Resist The Nazi Party’
text: Fox News’ Keith Ablow became the latest to chime in on Ben Carson’s controversial Holocaust remarks in an editorial published Saturday afternoon. While many have derided Ben’s statements regarding the recent Oregon shooting and the subsequent gun control debate, Keith stands firmly by the candidate in his column. Ablow, who was born a Jew, agreed...
